 156:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *         (0xFFFFFFFFU means that all the sectors have been correctly erased)
 157:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_flash_ex.c ****   *
